'''费氏弧菌'''（学名：''Aliivibrio fischeri''）是[[別弧菌屬|別弧菌屬]]的一种非自养、有運動性的细菌<ref>{{Cite book|title=Bergey's Manual of Determinative Bacteriology|last=Bergey|first=DH|publisher=Williams & Wilkins|year=1994|isbn=|editor-last=Holt|editor-first=JG|edition=9th|location=Baltimore|pages=}}</ref>，广泛分布于世界各大洋<ref name="Brock">{{cite book | veditors = Madigan M, Martinko J | title = Brock Biology of Microorganisms | edition = 11th | publisher = Prentice Hall | year = 2005 | isbn=978-0-13-144329-7 }}</ref>。它[[生物发光|可以发光]]，和许多海洋生物（如[[夏威夷短尾乌贼|夏威夷短尾乌贼]]）存在共生关系。其名来自德国微生物学家[[伯恩哈德·费舍尔|伯恩哈德·费舍尔]]的姓<ref>George M. Garrity: ''[[Bergey's_Manual_of_Systematic_Bacteriology|Bergey's Manual of Systematic Bacteriology]]''. 2. Auflage. Springer, New York, 2005, Volume 2: ''The Proteobacteria, Part B: The Gammaproteobacteria'' {{ISBN|0-387-24144-2}}</ref>。它的基因组测序工作在2004年完成<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|last=Ruby|first=E. G.|last2=Urbanowski|first2=M.|last3=Campbell|first3=J.|last4=Dunn|first4=A.|last5=Faini|first5=M.|last6=Gunsalus|first6=R.|last7=Lostroh|first7=P.|last8=Lupp|first8=C.|last9=McCann|first9=J.|date=2005-02-22|title=Complete genome sequence of Vibrio fischeri: A symbiotic bacterium with pathogenic congeners|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America|language=en|volume=102|issue=8|pages=3004–3009|doi=10.1073/pnas.0409900102|issn=0027-8424|pmc=549501|pmid=15703294|bibcode=2005PNAS..102.3004R}}</ref>。

它原属[[弧菌属|弧菌属]]，但[[rRNA|rRNA]]研究指出它应该属于[[別弧菌屬|別弧菌屬]]，因此在2007年划归后者<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Urbanczyk | first1 = H. | last2 = Ast | first2 = J. C. | last3 = Higgins | first3 = M. J. | last4 = Carson | first4 = J. | last5 = Dunlap | first5 = P. V. | title = Reclassification of ''Vibrio fischeri'', ''Vibrio logei'', ''Vibrio salmonicida'' and ''Vibrio wodanis'' as ''Aliivibrio fischeri'' gen. nov., comb. nov., ''Aliivibrio logei'' comb. nov., ''Aliivibrio salmonicida'' comb. nov. and ''Aliivibrio wodanis'' comb. nov. | journal = International Journal of Systematic and Evolutionary Microbiology | volume = 57 | issue = 12 | pages = 2823–2829 | year = 2007 | doi = 10.1099/ijs.0.65081-0 | pmid=18048732}}</ref>，但很多科学文献仍采用旧名''Vibrio fischeri''。
==基因组==
它包含两条染色体，[[基因组|基因组]][[基因测序|测序]]工作在2004年完成<ref name=":0" />。第一条包含290万个[[碱基对|碱基对]]，第二条包含130万个碱基对<ref name=":0" />。它的[[GC含量|GC含量]]是别弧菌属中最低的<ref name=":0" />。
